overview: After 2 years of hard work, the Stockholm Sabotage DVD is finally released for free. In this video, there are no still shots made on the trembling mobile phone, but a precise montage bringing together actions of the fine flower of the Scandinavian crews BST, FAME, VIM, OBH, SBR, MOA on the metro and trains of the suburb of Stockholm in Sweden.
tagline: Scandinavian crews BST, FAME, VIM, OBH, SBR, MOA on the metro and trains of the suburb of Stockholm in Sweden
title: Stockholm Sabotage
